tyle=\"color:#111111\">লবণ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">পেতে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">পারি<a name=\"_Hlk165371247\">।</a></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Cotton</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">&nbsp;dress is my favorite</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">.</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সুতির</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">পোশাক</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">আমার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">প্রিয়।</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #dddddd 1.0pt; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">5.Abstract Noun</span></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">(</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">গুণবাচক</span></span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বিশেষ্য)</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> Noun</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">দ্বারা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">কোন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ব্যক্তি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">কিংবা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বস্তুর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">গুণ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">কাজের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">নাম</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">কিংবা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">অবস্থা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">প্রকাশ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">হয়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তাকে</span></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Abstract </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Noun</span></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বলে।</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যেমন</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">,</span></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Liberty, anger, freedom, kindness, love, happiness, beauty<em>,</em></span></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ইত্যাদি।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Example</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">His&nbsp;<strong>kindness</strong>&nbsp;is his real beauty</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">.</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তাঁর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">দয়া</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তাঁর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">আসল</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সৌন্দর্য<a name=\"_Hlk164452840\">।</a></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Her&nbsp;<strong>beauty&nbsp;</strong>makes me crazy</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">.</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সৌন্দর্য</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">আমাকে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">পাগল</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তোলে।</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0.5in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>', NULL, 'classification of noun', 'noun-kake-ble-classification-of-noun-noun-kt-prkar-oo-ki-ki-udahrn-sh-bistarit', 1, 216, '1', '2024-05-03 23:29:50', '2024-06-20 17:31:55');
