(65, 7, 'classification of pronoun! Pronoun বা সর্বনাম কাকে বলে? কত প্রকার ও কি কি?', NULL, 'normal', 'Karim is a good boy; He goes to school every day. করিম ভালো ছেলে সে প্রতিদিন স্কুলে যায় ।  উপরের বাক্যে বলা হয়েছে করিম ভালো ছেলে সে প্রতিদিন স্কুলে যায় এখানে “সে” দিয়ে মূলত করিমকেই বলা হয়েছে ..', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Pronoun (সর্বনাম</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">):</span></span></strong>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সকল</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">শব্দ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">আমরা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">নামের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">পরিবর্তে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বসাই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তাকেই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Pronoun</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সর্বনাম</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বলে।</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যেমন</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">He, She, We etc</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Example</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Karim</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> is a good boy;</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> He</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> goes to school every day</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">. </span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করিম</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ভালো</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ছেলে</span></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সে</span></span></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">প্রতিদিন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">স্কুলে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0.5in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">উপরের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বাক্যে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বলা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">হয়েছে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করিম</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ভালো</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ছেলে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">প্রতিদিন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">স্কুলে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">এখানে </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">&ldquo;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">&rdquo; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">দিয়ে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">মূলত</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করিমকেই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বলা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">হয়েছে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বারবার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করিম</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বললে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বাক্যের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সৌন্দর্য</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">নষ্ট</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">হয়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তাই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">noun</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">এর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">পরিবর্তে</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">শব্দগুলো</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ব্যবহার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">হয়</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তাকেই</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> pronun</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বলে।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><a name=\"_Hlk164463248\"></a><a name=\"_heading=h.d0720kpl5k68\"></a><a name=\"_heading=h.yb3wzin4f70h\"></a></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Pronoun </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">প্রকারভেদ</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">1. person pronoun</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রুপ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আবার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দুইটি।</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Subjective (I, he, she etc) </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Objective (Him, her, me etc)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">My, our, his, her = Possessive adjective.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Me. them, him = objects pronoun</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border:none #eaecf0 1.0pt; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#1f3763\"><a name=\"_heading=h.1d4u6lwftcjo\"></a><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">2.Reflexive pronoun</span></span></strong></span></span></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Subject and object </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যদি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একই</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ব্যক্তি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বস্তুকে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বুঝায়</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তবে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তাকে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Reflexive pronoun </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বলে।</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">(myself / </span><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#202124\">আমিই</span></span></u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">, himself / </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তাঁকেই</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">, yourself / </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তুমাকেই</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">) </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এটি</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> preposition </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> object </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হিসেবে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ব্যবহৃত</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়৷</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border:none #eaecf0 1.0pt; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in\">\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:#1f3763\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">3.<a name=\"_Hlk165646829\">Relative</a> pronoun</span></span></strong></span></span></span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;(Who/which/that) </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এই</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শব্দগুলো</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যখন</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাক্যের</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">মাঝে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ব্যবহৃত</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়ে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দুইটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাক্যকে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একসাথে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">মিলিয়ে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অর্থ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">প্রকাশ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">করে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তখন </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Relative</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> pronoun</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বলে<a name=\"_Hlk165647176\">।</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">নিচের<strong> </strong>উদাহরণটি</span></span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">লক্ষ্য</span></span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করুন-</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Abdullah gave Karim money <strong>that</strong> he could start a new business <strong>which</strong> was actually a real collaboration <strong>who</strong> want to help a friend they can actually follow Abdullah.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">আবদুল্লাহ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করিমকে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">টাকা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">দিয়েছিল</span></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যেন</span></span></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">একটি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">নতুন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ব্যবসা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">শুরু</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করতে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">পারে</span></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যেটা</span></span></strong>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">আসলে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">একটি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সত্যিকারের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সহযোগিতা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ছিল</span></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যারা</span></span></strong><strong> </strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বন্ধুকে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সাহায্য</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করতে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">চায়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তারা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">আসলে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">আব্দুল্লাহকে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">অনুসরণ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">করতে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">পারে</span><span style=\"color:black\">।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">টিকা:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">That, Which, who,</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">উক্ত</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">শব্দগুলো</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যখন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ইংরেজি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বাক্যের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">ভিতরে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বসে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তখন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">তাদের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বাংলা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">অর্থ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">হয়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">এরকম</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">that</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> = </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যা</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> /</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যেন</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">/ </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><s