(66, 7, 'adjective meaning in bengali- Adjective কাকে বলে? Adjective এর প্রকারভেদ উদাহরণ সহ !', NULL, 'audio', 'যে সকল শব্দ দ্বারা কোন Noun বা Pronoun এর দোষ, গুণ, সংখ্যা, পরিমাণ, অবস্থা ইত্যাদি প্রকাশ করা হয় তাকে(adjective meaning in bengali) Adjective বলে।', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">যে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সকল</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">শব্দ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">দ্বারা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">কোন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Noun</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">বা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Pronoun</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">এর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">দোষ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">গুণ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">সংখ্যা</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">পরিমাণ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">অবস্থা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span 