\">বুঝাতে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <span style=\"font-size:18px\">on</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বসে।</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">যেমনঃ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:black\"> the office is on the 4th floor.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">অফিস</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">৪র্থ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তলায়।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><a name=\"_Hlk164510512\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">৪</span></span></a><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">।সীমানার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">উপর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বুঝাতে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <span style=\"font-size:18px\">on </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বসে।</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">যেমনঃ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"> The Buriganga is on the south of Dhaka</span>.</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ঢাকার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">দক্ষিণে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বুড়িগঙ্গা।</span></span></s