es,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">City </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শহর</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cities </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শহরগুলো</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;Story গল্প</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Stories </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">গল্প</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">গুলো</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">5.Noun </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শেষে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">f </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বা</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> fe </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থাকলে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">f </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বা</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> fe </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">স্থানে</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> ves </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যোগ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">করে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">plural </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">করতে</span> হয়। <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">&nbsp;কিছু</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Noun </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শেষ</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> f </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থাকলে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শুধু</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">s </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যুক্ত</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">করতে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp; Half&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Halves</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp; Self&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; selves</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">6. </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কয়েকটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ব্যতিক্রম</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পরিবর্তন।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp; Mouse </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ইঁদুর</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&