r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Throw</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:15.6pt; vertical-align:top; width:136.9pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">নিক্ষেপ</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">করা</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:15.6pt; vertical-align:top; width:121.5pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Threw</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:15.6pt; vertical-align:top; width:122.5pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Thrown</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"height:15.6pt; vertical-align:top; width:110.2pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Dream</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:15.6pt; vertical-align:top; width:136.9pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">স্বপ্ন</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">দেখা</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:15.6pt; vertical-align:top; width:121.5pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Dreamt</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"height:15.6pt; vertical-align:top; width:122.5pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Dreamt</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">(আমার লেখা&nbsp; ইংলিশ এর উপর অন্য একটি বই রয়েছে যে বইটিতে&nbsp; প্রচুর Bangla অর্থসহ </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">vocabulary, </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">verb</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ও,</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">verb</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তিনটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রূপ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">pronunciation audio &nbsp;(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">উচ্চারন</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">) </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সহকারে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দেওয়া</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আছে। </span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আপনার</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">English vocabulary </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সমৃদ্ধ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">করতে</span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পড়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পরামর্শ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থাকলো।)</span></span></span></p>', NULL, 'english vocabulary meaning in bengali', 'english-vocabulary-meaning-in-bengali-verb-er-tinti-form-oo-bangla-orthsh', 1, 47, '1', '2024-05-24 17:43:09', '2024-06-21 02:49:54');
INSERT INTO `book_items` (`id`, `chapter_id`, `title`, `sub_title`, `type`, `short_details`, `details`, `audio_text`, `keyword`, `slug`, `status`, `pageview`, `added_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(85, 11, 'present indefinite tense bangla  অথবা simple present tense শেখুন বিস্তারিত! !', NULL, 'normal', 'Present indefinite tense -কোন কাজ বর্তমানে হয় বোঝালে.. structure : Subject+Verb1 + Object.  present indefinite tense example:  - আমি ভাত খাই – I eat rice.', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:green\">Voice এর</span></span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:green\">সংজ্ঞা</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:green\"> :</span></span></strong>&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">Voice</span></strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">অর্থ</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">বাচ্য</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"> , </span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">ক্রিয়া</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">প্রকাশের</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">ভঙ্গিমাকেই</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">&nbsp;<strong>Voice</strong>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">বা</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">বাচ্য</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">বলে</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">নিচের</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">বাক্য</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">দুটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">পড়</span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">I eat a mango</span> (আমি</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">একটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">আম</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">খাই</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">) ।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">A mango is eaten by me</span> (আমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">দ্বারা</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">একটা</span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">আম</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">খাওয়া</span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">হয়</span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">)।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><span style=\"color:black\">There are two types of voice:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><span style=\"color:black\">Active voice.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><span style=\"color:black\">Passive voice.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><strong><span style=\"color:#032d4c\">Active voice:</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">যে <span style=\"font-size:20px\">sentence </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <span style=\"font-size:20px\">subject </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">নিজে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সক্রিয়</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বা</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> active </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">হয়ে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">কাজ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সম্পন্ন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">করে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <span style=\"font-size:20px\">sentence</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> verb </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এর</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <span style=\"font-size:20px\">Active voice </span>হয়।</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Structure:</span></span></strong><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><strong>Subject + verb + object.</strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><span style=\"color:black\">Example: I do the work.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><strong><span style=\"color:#032d4c\">Passive voice:</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">যে sentence </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> subject </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">নিজে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">কাজটি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">করে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">না</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বরং</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> object </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">কাজটি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ওপর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এসে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">পড়ে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তখন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <span style=\"font-size:20px\">sentence</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এ</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> verb </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এর</span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <span style=\"font-size:20px\">passive voice</span> হয়।</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Structure:</span></strong><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:black\"><strong>Object + be verb + verb </strong></span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এর <span style=\"font-size:20px\">past participle+ by+ subject.</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9\"><span style=\"color:black\">Example: The work is done by me.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">active</span> এবং<span style=\"font-size:20px\"> passive voice </span>উভয়ের আবার ১২ টি প্রকার রয়েছে <span style=\"font-size:20px\">active voice </span>কে&nbsp; মূলত <span style=\"font-size:20px\">tense&nbsp;</span> বলা হয়ে থাকে এই অধ্যায় <span style=\"font-size:20px\">tense</span>&nbsp; বা <span style=\"font-size:20px\">active voice</span>&nbsp; নিয়ে বিস্তারিত আলোচনা করা হলো পরবর্তী কোনো একটি অধ্যায়ে <span style=\"font-size:20px\">passive voice&nbsp;</span> নিয়ে আলোচনা করা হবে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">* </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Present indefinite</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কোন কাজ বর্তমানে হয়, অভ্যাসগত সত্য বা চিরসত্য বোঝালে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Present Indefinite Tense</span> হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় ক্রিয়ার শেষে , অ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থেকে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ঔ</span> &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">১১</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">টি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">স্বরবর্ণের পূর্ণরূপ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অথবা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সংক্ষিপ্ত</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রূপ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থাকবে</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">present indefinite tense structure</span>&nbsp;:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Subject + Verb 1 + Object.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">present indefinite tense example:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি ভাত খাই </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; I eat rice.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">- </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আমি স্কুলে যাই </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; I go to school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">- </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সে প্রতিদিন স্কুলে যায় </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; He goes to school every day.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">- </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তুমি বই পড় </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; You read a book.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">- </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সে প্রতিদিন রাত দশ টায় ঘুমাতে যায় </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; He goes to bed at ten pm every day.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">- </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সূর্য পূর্ব দিকে উদিত হয় </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; The sun rises in the East.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">- </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পানি শূন্য ডিগ্রি সেন্ট্রিগ্রেডে জমাট বাধে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; Water freezes at 0&deg; centegrade.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Note - Subject third person singular number (he, she, it, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কোন ব্যক্তি, বস্তু, জায়গা বা প্রাণীর নাম) বোঝালে <span style=\"font-size:20px\">verb </span>এর শেষে <span style=\"font-size:20px\">s </span>বা <span style=\"font-size:20px\">es</span>বসে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">present indefinite tense exercise:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">She eats an apple every day.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">সে প্রতিদিন একটি আপেল খায়।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">They play football on Sundays.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">তারা রবিবার ফুটবল খেলে।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">He goes to school by bus.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">সে বাসে করে স্কুলে যায়।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">We watch TV in the evening.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">আমরা সন্ধ্যায় টিভি দেখি।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">The sun rises in the east.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">সূর্য পূর্ব দিকে ওঠে।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Birds fly in the sky.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">পাখিরা আকাশে উড়ে।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">She reads a book every night.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">সে প্রতিরাত একটি বই পড়ে।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">They visit their grandparents every month.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">তারা প্রতি মাসে তাদের দাদু-দিদার বাড়ি যায়।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">The baby cries a lot.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">শিশুটি অনেক কান্নাকাটি করে।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">We drink water when we are thirsty.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">আমরা তৃষ্ণার্ত হলে পানি পান করি।</span></span></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">(লক্ষ্য</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">করুন</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">প্রতিটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">বাক্যের</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">কাজের</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">শেষ</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">বর্ণতে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">সংক্ষিপ্ত</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">অথবা</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">পূর্ণ</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">স্বরবর্ণ</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">রয়েছে)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Note - Subject third person singular number (he, she, it, Rahim</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">. বোঝালে) </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">verb</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> এর শেষে </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">s</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বা </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">es</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> বসে।&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">S sh, x , ch, c </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">সাধারনত</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">উক্ত</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">লেটার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">গুলো</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">কোন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">শব্দের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">শেষে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">থাকলে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">es</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">যোগ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">করতে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">হয়।</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">এছাড়া</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">শুধু</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">s</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">যুক্ত</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">করলেই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">Plural</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#282829\">হবে।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>&nbsp;# টিকা</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">The = </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">টি</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the question</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">প্রশ্নটি</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">This </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দিস</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">) </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">= </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এইটি</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;this question </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এই</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">প্রশ্নটি</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">That question </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">= ঐ প্রশ্নটি, </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Those questions</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> = ঐ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">প্রশ্নগুলো</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">(That </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যদি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাক্যের</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ভিতরে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বসে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তাহলে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এটার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অর্থ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হবে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যেটা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যাকে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এরকম)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">These (</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দিজ</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">) = </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এই</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">গুলো</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">these questions&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এই</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">প্রশ্নগুলো</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Those questions </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">= ঐ গুলো, </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Those questions</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> = ঐ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">প্রশ্নগুলো</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'present indefinite tense bangla', 'present-indefinite-tense-bangla-othba-simple-present-tense-sekhun-bistarit', 1, 54, '1', '2024-05-25 16:24:53', '2024-06-21 04:16:50'),
(87, 11, 'present continuous tense-চলমান বর্তমান কাল সহজ পদ্ধতিতে! উদাহরণ সহ!', NULL, 'audio', 'Present continuous tense-বর্তমানে কোন কাজ চলতেছে..present continuous tense examples:  - আমি ভাত খাইতেছি – I am eating rice', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় ক্রিয়া বা </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">verb </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর শেষে তেছি, তেছ, তেছে, তেছেন, চ্ছ, চ্ছি, চ্ছে, চ্ছেন, , ইত্যাদি থাকে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Structure:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Subject + am /is / are+ verb </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সঙ্গে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">ing + object.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">&nbsp;present continuous tense examples:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">- আমি ভাত খাইতেছি &ndash; <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">I am eating rice.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">- আমি স্কুলে যাইতেছি &ndash;<span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"> I am going to school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">- সে স্কুলে যাইতেছে &ndash;<span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"> He is going to school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">- তুমি/ তোমরা বই পড়িতেছ &ndash; <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">You are reading book.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">- আমি আজ রাতে ঢাকা যাব &ndash; <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">I am going to Dhaka tonight. (Near future)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">- আপনি কি আজ বিকালে মীটিং এ আসছেন &ndash; <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">Are you coming to the meeting this afternoon? (Near future)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">Note - I</span> এর পর <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">am</span> বসবে। <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">He, She, it </span>এবং অন্যসব <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">third person singular number</span> এর পর <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">is</span> বসবে। <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">We, you, they</span> এবং <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">Plural subject</span> এর শেষে <span style=\"font-size:16.5pt\">are</span> বসে।</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"># টিকা</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">#</span>সাধারণত <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">To</span> এর পর <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">verb</span> আসলে <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">verb 1 </span>হয় সেই সাথে বাংলায়&nbsp; অর্থ হবে-&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">To eat</span> খাইতে/ খাওয়ার&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">Not to eat</span> না খাইতে /না খাওয়ার &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">To go</span> যাইতে/যাওয়ার&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Not to go </span>না যাইতে /না যাওয়ার &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\">To come</span> আসতে / আসার&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Not to come </span>না আসতে /না আসার</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">&nbsp;(</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">টিকা</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অংশটি ভালোভাবে বার বার পড়তে হবে । এবং অন্যান্য শব্দ দিয়ে অর্থ করার চেষ্টা&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; করতে হবে)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Note:</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কয়েকটি</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> phrasal verb </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">বা</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> adjective </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সাথে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যদি</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">to</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থাকে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তাহলে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">to </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পর</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;Verb </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সাথে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">ing </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থাকতে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পারে। </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যেমন</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> key to, admit to.</span><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></span></span></p>', NULL, 'present continuous tense-', 'present-continuous-tense-clman-brtman-kal-shj-pddhtite-udahrn-sh', 1, 42, '1', '2024-05-25 20:08:15', '2024-06-21 14:45:09'),
(88, 11, 'what is present perfect tense - গঠনপ্রণালী ! present perfect tense examples -উদাহরণ', NULL, 'normal', 'Present Perfect Tense -বাংলায় ক্রিয়ার শেষে য়াছ, য়াছে, য়াছি, , য়াছেন present perfect tense examples -আমি ভাত খাইয়াছি – I have eaten rice. present perfect tense structure- Subject + have/has + past participle + object.', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><strong>Present Perfect Tense:</strong></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কোন কাজ শেষ হয়েছে অথচ তার ফল এখনও বর্তমান আছে (অপ্রকাশিত), এরূপ বোঝালে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Present perfect tense </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলা বাক্যের&nbsp;&nbsp;ক্রিয়ার বা কাজের শেষে য়াছ, য়াছে, য়াছি, , য়াছেন, য়েছ, , ইয়াছি, ইয়াছে, ইয়েছ, ইয়াছেন ইত্যাদি বসে। </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Present perfect tense </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">present perfect tense structure:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Subject + have/has + past participle + object.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">present perfect tense examples:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি ভাত খাইয়াছি &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">I have eaten rice.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি স্কুলে গিয়েছি &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">I have gone to school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে স্কুলে গিয়েছি &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He has gone to school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি ভাত খাইনি &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">I have not eaten rice.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- তারা/তাহারা কাজটি করিয়াছে &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">They have done the work.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে ঘণ্টার পর ঘণ্টা পড়েছে &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He/she has studied for hours.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- তারা এইমাত্র ফুটবল খেলিয়াছে - </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">They have just played football.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে এইমাত্র ফুটবল খেলিয়াছে &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He has just played football.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Note - Subject third person singular number (he, she, it, bird,&nbsp; Rahim</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">) বোঝালে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">has</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> বসবে । </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">I, we, you, they </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং অন্যসব </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">plural subject </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর শেষে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">have</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> বসবে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Present Perfect Tense, present perfect tense examples, present perfect tense structure', 'what-is-present-perfect-tense-gthnprnalee-present-perfect-tense-examples-udahrn', 1, 33, '1', '2024-05-28 04:56:46', '2024-06-21 22:32:40');
INSERT INTO `book_items` (`id`, `chapter_id`, `title`, `sub_title`, `type`, `short_details`, `details`, `audio_text`, `keyword`, `slug`, `status`, `pageview`, `added_by`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(89, 11, 'present perfect continuous tense কাকে বলে? present perfect continuous tense examples-উদাহরণ', NULL, 'normal', 'present perfect continuous tense-অতীতকালে কোন কাজ নির্দিষ্ট একটি সময়ে আরম্ভ হয়ে এখনও চলছে বুঝালে present perfect continuous tense examples ..', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Present Perfect Continuous Tense:</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অতীতকালে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কোন</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কাজ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">নির্দিষ্ট</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সময়ে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আরম্ভ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়ে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এখনও</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">চলছে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বুঝালে</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> Present perfect continuous tense </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় ক্রিয়ার শেষে তেছ, তেছি,তেছে, তেছেন, চ্ছ, চ্ছি, চ্ছে, চ্ছেন, এবং তার সাথে সময়ের উল্লেখ থাকে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">present perfect continuous tense Structure:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Subject + has been/have been + main verb + ing + since/from/for + object.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">present perfect continuous tense examples:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি দুই দিন ধরে কাজটি করিতেছি &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">I have been doing this work for two days.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে দুই ঘণ্টা যাবৎ পড়িতেছে &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He has been reading for two hours</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">. (নির্দিষ্ট সময়)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে সকাল থেকে পড়িতেছে&ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He has been reading since mourning.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে তিন বছর যাবৎ এই স্কুলে পড়িতেছে &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He/She has been reading in this school for three years.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- ছেলেবেলা হতে সে এখানে বাস করিতেছে &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He has been living here from his boyhood.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- ফাহিম গত সোমবার হইতে জ্বরে ভুগিতেছে &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Fahim has been suffering from fever since sunday last.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Note - Subject third person singular number (he, she, it, Rahim </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">) বোঝালে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">has been </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বসবে । </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">I, we, you, they </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং অন্যসব </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">plural subject </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর শেষে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">have been </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বসবে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Note - </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এক্ষেত্রে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">since</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> ব্যাবহার হবে শুধুমাত্র </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">point of time (past tense) </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর ক্ষেত্রে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দিন কিংবা বার এর ক্ষেত্রে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">since or from </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়। সব </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">tense</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> এর ক্ষেত্রে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">from</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> ব্যাবহার করা যায়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অনেক বেশি সময় এর ক্ষেত্রে, কোন ব্যাক্তিগত ক্ষেত্রে <span style=\"font-size:20px\">from</span> ব্যাবহার হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Period of time </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর ক্ষেত্রে অর্থাৎ কোন নির্দিষ্ট সময়ের ব্যাপ্তি বোঝাতে <span style=\"font-size:20px\">for </span>ব্যাবহার হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">reading for two hours. </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">(নির্দিষ্ট সময়)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সে সকাল থেকে পড়িতেছে</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; He has been reading since mourning.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সে তিন বছর যাবৎ এই স্কুলে পড়িতেছে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; He/She has been reading in this school for three years.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">&nbsp;ছেলেবেলা হতে সে এখানে বাস করিতেছে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; He has been living here from his boyhood.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ফাহিম গত সোমবার হইতে জ্বরে ভুগিতেছে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; Fahim has been suffering from fever since sunday last.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">#&nbsp; টিকা</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">To</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ব্যাতিত</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সকল</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">preposition</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পর</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">verb</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আসলে</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> verb </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সাথে</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> ing</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থাকবে এবং বাংলা&nbsp; অর্থ যেমন হবে,</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Eating</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়া</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খেয়ে</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাইয়া</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাইতে</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">,খাইতে&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">not Eating </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">না খাওয়া, না খেয়ে,না খাইয়া,না খাইতে,না খাইতে&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></span></pre>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">In not eating </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়া</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সময় </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">/</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">মধ্যে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">With eating </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সাথে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">With not eating </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">না </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সাথে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">For eating </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">জন্য</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">For not eating </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">না&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">জন্য</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Before eating </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পূর্বে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Before not eating </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পূর্বে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">After eating&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">না</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পর</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Without eating </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খওয়া</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ছারা</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Without not eating </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">না</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খওয়া</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ছারা</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Of eating </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Of not eating </span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">না&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'present perfect continuous tense, present perfect continuous tense examples', 'present-perfect-continuous-tense-kake-ble-present-perfect-continuous-tense-examples-udahrn', 1, 48, '1', '2024-05-28 16:59:18', '2024-06-22 03:38:49'),
(90, 11, 'Let\'s practice on the present  tense চলুন বর্তমান ইনফিনিটিভ কালের অনুশীলন করি', NULL, 'normal', 'My father has sleeps / my younger brother is eating rice   আমার বাবা ঘুমিয়ে পড়েছে/ ছোট ভাই ভাত খাইতেছ,  The morning passes peacefully. Rina feels happy and content. সকালটি শান্তভাবে কাটে। রিনা সুখী এবং তৃপ্ত বোধ করে।', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Nirmala UI&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">1. My father has sleeps / my younger brother is eating rice&nbsp;&nbsp; / Mother has been caressing me for one hour /so that / I study</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আমার বাবা ঘুমিয়ে পড়েছে/ ছোট ভাই ভাত খাইতেছ/ মা এক ঘন্টা ধরে আমাকে আদর করতেছে/ যাতে / পড়ালেখা করি</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">2. Rahim&#39;s father has given me/ this mango/ to eat/ because /he knows/ I like mango /for this /Rahim&#39;s younger brother has been seeking me since 8 pm/ to ask me / about mango and his father/ but I am sleeping now / not to go/ in front him</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রহিমের বাবা আমাকে এই আমটি&nbsp; দিয়েছেন /&nbsp; খেতে / কারণ /তিনি জানেন /আমি আম পছন্দ করি/ এই জন্য/ রহিমের ছোট ভাই রাত ৮টা থেকে আমাকে খুঁজতেছে / আম এবং তার বাবার সম্পর্কে/&nbsp; জিজ্ঞেস করতে/&nbsp; কিন্তু আমি এখন ঘুমাচ্ছি /না যাইতে/ তার সামনে </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">3. Mithila accepts a challenge/ that/ she is driving cycle / to win/ in a cycling event /she and his brother have been trying/ to win /in a cycling competition / for 5 years </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">-</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">মিথিলা একটি চ্যালেঞ্জ গ্রহণ করে/ যে/ সে সাইকেল চালাচ্ছে/ জয়ী হতে/ সাইক্লিং ইভেন্টে/ সে এবং তার ভাই চেষ্টা করছে/ জয়ের জন্য/ সাইক্লিং প্রতিযোগিতায়/ 5 বছর ধরে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">4.</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Rina wakes up early every morning. She smiles at the sun and breathes in the fresh air. Today, she decides to visit the nearby park.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রিনা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">প্রতিদিন</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সকালে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তাড়াতাড়ি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ওঠে।</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সূর্যের</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দিকে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তাকিয়ে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হাসে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তাজা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাতাস</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">গ্রহণ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">করে।</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আজ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পাশের</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পার্কে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সিদ্ধান্ত</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">নেয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">She puts on her favorite blue dress and steps out. The park is quiet, with only the sound of birds chirping. Rina sits on a bench and watches the children play.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">প্রিয়</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">নীল</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পোশাক</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পরে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাইরে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রাখে।</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পার্কটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শান্ত</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শুধুমাত্র</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পাখির</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ডাক</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শোনা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যায়।</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রিনা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বেঞ্চে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বসে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শিশুদের</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খেলতে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দেখে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">A little girl comes up to her and offers a flower. Rina accepts it with a warm smile.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ছোট</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">মেয়ে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কাছে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আসে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ফুল</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দেয়।</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রিনা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">উষ্ণ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হাসি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দিয়ে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">গ্রহণ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">করে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">The morning passes peacefully. Rina feels happy and content. She knows today will be a good day.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সকালটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শান্তভাবে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কাটে।</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রিনা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সুখী</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তৃপ্ত</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বোধ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">করে।</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">জানে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আজকের</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দিনটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ভালো</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হবে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'practice present indefinite tense', 'lets-practice-on-the-present-infinitive-tense-clun-brtman-infinitiv-kaler-onuseeln-kri', 1, 38, '1', '2024-05-28 18:49:34', '2024-06-21 09:35:29'),
(91, 11, 'past indefinite tense Bangla - কাকে বলে? past indefinite tense examples উদাহরণ সহ! বিস্তারিত!', NULL, 'normal', 'past indefinite tense Bangla - কাকে বলে? past indefinite tense examples আমি ভাত খাইয়াছিলাম/খেয়েছিলাম – I ate rice.!', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\">Past Indefinite Tense </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অতীত কালের কোন কাজ বোঝাতে বা অতীতের কোন অভ্যাস বোঝাতে, যার ফল এখন আর বিদ্যমান নেই তাকে <span style=\"font-size:20px\">Past Indefinite Tense</span> বলে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় ক্রিয়ার শেষে ল, লাম, ত, তাম, তে, তেন এদের যে কোন একটি যোগ থাকে। যেমন ( করেছিল, করিয়াছিল, করেছিলাম, করিয়াছিলাম, করেছিলে, করিয়া ছিলে, করেছিলেন, করিয়াছিলেন, পড়িল, পড়িলাম, পড়িলেন, পড়িত, পরিতেন, ইত্যাদি)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">past indefinite tense structure:</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">গঠনপ্রণালী</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Subject + verb 2 + object.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">past indefinite tense examples</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি ভাত খাইয়াছিলাম/খেয়েছিলাম &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">I ate rice.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি স্কুলে গেছিলাম/গিয়েছিলাম &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">I went to school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে স্কুলে গেছিলো/গিয়েছিল &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He went to school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- তুমি/ তোমরা কাজটি করেছিলে/করিয়াছিলে- </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">You did the work.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- তার ছেলেবেলা লন্ডনেকেটেছিল &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He spent his boyhood in London.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- লুনা একটি গান গেয়েছিল &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Luna sang a song.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে ফুটবল খেলেছিল &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He played football.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'past indefinite tense Bangla, past indefinite tense examples', 'past-indefinite-tense-bangla-kake-ble-past-indefinite-tense-examples-udahrn-sh-bistarit', 1, 34, '1', '2024-05-28 19:50:38', '2024-06-21 13:33:45'),
(92, 11, 'past continuous tense কাকে বলে? উদাহরণ সহ! বিস্তারিত!', NULL, 'normal', 'অতীতকালে কোন কাজ কিছুক্ষণ ধরে চলছিল এরূপ বোঝালে Past continuous tense হয়।Structure  Subject + was/were + main verb + ing + object.', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Past Continuous Tense</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অতীতকালে কোন কাজ কিছুক্ষণ ধরে চলছিল এরূপ বোঝালে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Past continuous tense </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় ক্রিয়ার শেষে তেছিল, তেছিলাম, তেছিলে, তেছিলেন, চ্ছিল, চ্ছিলে, চ্ছিলেন, যে কোন একটি যুক্ত থাকে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">&nbsp;past continuous tense Structure</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Subject + was/were +&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">verb </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সঙ্গে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">ing </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> + object.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Example</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি ভাত খাইতেছিলাম/খাচ্ছিলাম &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">I was eating rice.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে স্কুলে যাইতেছিল/যাচ্ছিল &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He was going to school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- তারা ফুটবল খেলিতেছিল/খেলছিল &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">They were playing football.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- গতকাল সন্ধায় সে ঢাকা যাইতেছিল &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">He was going to Dhaka last evening.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি একা একা গান গাইতেছিলাম &ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">I was singing song alone.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Note - subject first person and third person singular number </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হলে</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> was </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বসবে। </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">we, you, they </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং অন্যান্য </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">plural number </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর শেষে </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">were</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> বসবে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">#&nbsp; টিকা</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"># </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Having problems </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সমস্যা হচ্ছে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Having a chat with him </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তার সাথে আড্ডা&nbsp; হচ্ছে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">To have a problem in here </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এখানে একটি সমস্যা আছে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"># Like, মত, যেমন</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Like you তোমার মত</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Like I say</span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যেমন আমি বলি</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"># </span><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Preposition</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"> + </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#e4e6eb\"><span style=\"color:#050505\">possessive case </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#e4e6eb\"><span style=\"color:#050505\">+ V1ing</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">In my eating -</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">মধ্যে/আমার খাওয়ার সময়</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">With my eating -</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সাথে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">For your eating -</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তুমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">জন্যে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Without their eating- </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তাদের</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়া</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ছারা</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Without your mother cooking - </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তুমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">মা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রান্না</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">করা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ছাড়া।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Before your grandmother&#39;s father going - </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তুমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দাদির</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাবার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পূর্বে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">&nbsp;(এই অংশটি ভালোভাবে বার বার পড়তে হবে । এবং </span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অন্যান্য শব্দ দিয়ে অর্থ করার চেষ্টা করতে হবে)</span></span></span></p>', NULL, 'past continuous tense', 'past-continuous-tense-kake-ble-udahrn-sh-bistarit', 1, 51, '1', '2024-05-30 00:02:45', '2024-06-22 16:36:13'),
(93, 11, 'past perfect tense কাকে বলে? past perfect tense examples উদাহরণ সহ! বিস্তারিত!', NULL, 'audio', 'past perfect tense-অতীত কালে দুটি কাজ সম্পন্ন হয়ে থাকলে তাদের মধ্যে যেটি আগে ঘটেছিল তা Past perfect tense examples - He had come home before I ate rice.', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">অতীত কালে দুটি কাজ সম্পন্ন হয়ে থাকলে তাদের মধ্যে যেটি আগে ঘটেছিল তা </span><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Past perfect tense</span><span style=\"font-size:18px\"> হয় এবং যেটি পরে হয়েছিল তা </span><span style=\"font-size:20px\">simple past tense </span><span style=\"font-size:18px\">হয়।</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়: বাক্যে দুটি কাজ থাকবে</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\">past perfect tense structure</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\">1st subject + had + verb এর past participle + 2nd subject + verb এর past form +2nd object.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Or</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\">1st subject + had + verb এর past participle + simple past tense</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\">past perfect tense examples</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">- আমি ভাত খাওয়ার পূর্বে সে বাড়ি আসল &ndash; He had come home before I ate rice.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">- আমি স্কুলে যাওয়ার পূর্বে সে মারা গেল &ndash; He had died before I went to school.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">- ঘণ্টা পড়ার পূর্বে তারা স্টেশনে পৌঁছল &ndash; They had reached the station before the bell rang.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">- ডাক্তার আসিবার পূর্বে রোগীটি মারা গেল &ndash; The patient had died before the doctor came.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">- ডাক্তার আসিবার পরে রোগীটি মারা গেল &ndash; The doctor had come before the patient died.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">- বিছানায় শুতে যাবার পূর্বে আমি দরজাটা বন্ধ করিলাম &ndash; I had shut the door before I got into bed.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">#&nbsp; টিকা</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"># Having problems সমস্যা হচ্ছে</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Having a chat with him তার সাথে আড্ডা&nbsp; হচ্ছে</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">To have a problem in here এখানে একটি সমস্যা আছে</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"># Like, মত, যেমন</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Like you তোমার মত</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Like I say</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">যেমন আমি বলি</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\"># Preposition + possessive case + V1ing</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">In my eating -আমার খাওয়ার মধ্যে/আমার খাওয়ার সময়</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">With my eating -আমার খাওয়ার সাথে</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">For your eating -তুমার খাওয়ার জন্যে</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Without their eating- তাদের খাওয়া ছারা</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Without your mother cooking - তুমার মা রান্না করা ছাড়া।</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Before your grandmother&#39;s father going - তুমার দাদির বাবার যাওয়ার পূর্বে</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&nbsp;(এই অংশটি ভালোভাবে বার বার পড়তে হবে । এবং অন্যান্য শব্দ দিয়ে অর্থ করার চেষ্টা করতে হবে)</span></p>', NULL, 'past perfect tense, past perfect tense examples ,past perfect tense structure', 'past-perfect-tense-kake-ble-past-perfect-tense-examples-udahrn-sh-bistarit', 1, 38, '1', '2024-05-30 04:51:18', '2024-06-21 15:45:12'),
(94, 11, 'past perfect continuous tense কাকে বলে?past perfect continuous tense examples  উদাহরণ সহ!', NULL, 'audio', 'past perfect tense-অতীত কালে দুটি কাজ সম্পন্ন হয়ে থাকলে তাদের মধ্যে যেটি আগে ঘটেছিল তা Past perfect tense examples - He had come home before I ate rice.', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অতীতকালে কোন কাজ কোন বিশেষ সময়ের পূর্বে আরম্ভ হয়ে সেই সময় পর্যন্ত চলছিল বোঝালে </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Past perfect continuous tense </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়। এখানে যদি দুটি ক্রিয়া উল্লেখ থাকে তাহলে যে কাজটি আগে চলছিল তা </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Past perfect continuous tense </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">বাংলায়</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ক্রিয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">শেষে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তেছিল</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তেছিলে</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তেছিলাম</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তেছিলেন</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">চ্ছিল</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">চ্ছিলাম</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">চ্ছিলে</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">চ্ছিলেন</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এদের</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">যে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কোন</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">উল্লেখ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থাকলে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এবং</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">অতীতের</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">একটি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সময়</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">উল্লেখ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">থাকে।</span> </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">&nbsp;past perfect continuous tense Structure</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">1st subject + had been + verb1 </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">এর </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">সঙ্গে </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">ing</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"> + 1st object + 2nd subject + verb </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">এর </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">past form + 2nd object.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">past perfect continuous tense examples</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- সে যখন আসিল তখন আমি ভাত খাইতেছিলাম </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; I had been eating rice when he came.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- ঘণ্টা পড়ার পূর্বে আমরা খেলিতেছিলাম </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; We had been playing before the bell rang.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- আমি যখন তার সাথে দেখা করতে গেলাম তখন সে বই পরিতেছিল </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&ndash; </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">He had been reading book when I went to meet with him/her.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">- তুমি যখন তোমার বন্ধুর বাড়িতে গিয়েছিলে তখন তোমার মা তোমার জন্য অপেক্ষা করিতেছিল </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">&ndash; Your mother had been waiting for you when you went to your friend&rsquo;s home.</span></span></span></p>', NULL, 'past perfect continuous tense,past perfect continuous tense examples', 'past-perfect-continuous-tense-kake-blepast-perfect-continuous-tense-examples-udahrn-sh', 1, 42, '1', '2024-05-30 05:07:08', '2024-06-21 21:55:19');
