(95, 11, 'Let\'s practice on past tense চলুন  present tense অনুশীলন করি', NULL, 'normal', 'অনুশীলন করি past simple, past  continuous and past perfect tense and past perfect continuous', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">1.M<span style=\"color:black\">y uncle came to my room/ in my eating / for me giving/ those pens /after his sleeping /He was coming to my room/ again/ before my eating launch</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">&nbsp;আমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">চাচা</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রুমে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এসেছিলেন </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">/ </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সময়</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> / </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আমাকে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">দেওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">জন্য</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">/ </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ঐ</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">কলমগুলো </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">/ </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">ঘুমানোর</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">পর </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">/ </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">তিনি</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আমার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">রুমে</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আসতেছিলেন </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">/ </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আবার </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">/ </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আমার</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> দুপুরের </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">খাওয়ার</span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">আগে</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">2.</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">যেমন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তুমি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বলেছিলে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">as you said</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তোমার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বাবার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সাথে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:black\">with your </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">father</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তোমার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ছোট</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ভাই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">আসার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">আগে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">b<span style=\"font-size:20px\">efore your younger brother coming</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বাজারে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">to market</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">যাওয়ার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">জন্য</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <span style=\"font-size:20px\">for going</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">কিনতে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> <span style=\"font-size:20px\">to buy</span> </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">একটি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">হলুদ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">গাড়ি</span></span><span style=\"font-size:20px\"> <span style=\"color:black\">a yellow car </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তোমার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">চাচার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">উপহার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">দেওয়া</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">টাকা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:black\">your uncle&rsquo;s gifted money </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">দিয়া</span></span><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:black\"> giving&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">3.You loved me / as I wanted from you / in here / to have a problem / in your respecting / doing/ over excess/doing / without my permission </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তুমি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">আমাকে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ভালোবেসেছিলে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> /</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">যেমন</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">আমি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তোমার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">কাছ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">থেকে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">চেয়ে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ছিলাম</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> /</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এখানে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">/</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">একটি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সমস্যা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">আছে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> /</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">তোমার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সম্মানে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">মধ্যে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> / </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">অতিরিক্ত</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">/ করো / </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">আমার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">অনুমতি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ছাড়া /</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">4. I slept / to just rest / after eating rice / with my father&#39;s friend / without&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; any hassle&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">আমি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ঘুমিয়েছি</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">/</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">শুধু</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বিশ্রাম</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">নিতে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">/</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ভাত</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> খাওয়া ছাড়া /</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বাবার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বন্ধুর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সাথে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">/</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">কোন</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ঝামেলা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ছাড়াই</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">5.&nbsp;</span>Once, Maria decided to get a medical pedicure because her feet were in pain. She visited a specialist, who carefully examined her feet. Maria felt nervous initially, but the specialist assured her everything would be fine. The procedure began with a thorough cleaning of her feet, removing any dead skin and calluses. Maria noticed an immediate difference; her feet felt lighter and more comfortable.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">একদিন, মারিয়া একটি মেডিকেল পেডিকিউর করার সিদ্ধান্ত নেয় কারণ তার পায়ে ব্যথা হচ্ছিল। সে একজন বিশেষজ্ঞের কাছে গেল, যিনি তার পা ভালোভাবে পরীক্ষা করলেন। মারিয়া প্রথমে নার্ভাস ছিল, কিন্তু বিশেষজ্ঞ তাকে আশ্বস্ত করলেন যে সবকিছু ঠিকঠাক হবে। প্রক্রিয়াটি তার পা ভালোভাবে পরিষ্কার করার মাধ্যমে শুরু হয়, যেকোনো মৃত ত্বক এবং শক্ত চামড়া অপসারণ করা হয়। মারিয়া তাৎক্ষণিক পার্থক্য অনুভব করল; তার পা হালকা এবং আরো আরামদায়ক মনে হচ্ছিল।</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">After the procedure, the specialist gave Maria tips on how to take care of her feet. Maria followed the advice diligently and noticed her feet were healthier and pain-free. She was grateful for the medical pedicure and continued to take care of her feet.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">প্রক্রিয়ার পর, বিশেষজ্ঞ মারিয়াকে তার পায়ের যত্ন নেওয়ার জন্য কিছু পরামর্শ দিলেন। মারিয়া মনোযোগ দিয়ে সেই পরামর্শগুলি মেনে চলল এবং লক্ষ্য করল যে তার পা আরো সুস্থ এবং ব্যথামুক্ত। সে মেডিকেল পেডিকিউরের জন্য কৃতজ্ঞ ছিল এবং তার পায়ের যত্ন নিতে থাকে।</span></span></p>', NULL, 'past simple, past  continuous and past perfect tense and past perfect continuous', 'lets-practice-on-the-present-infinitive-tense-clun-present-tense-onuseeln-kri', 1, 21, '1', '2024-06-01 20:38:29', '2024-06-22 20:23:26'),
(96, 11, 'Future Indefinite Tense  কাকে বলে? Future Indefinite tense examples উদাহরণ সহ! বিস্তারিত!', NULL, 'normal', 'বাংলায় ক্রিয়ার শেষে বে, ব, বা, বি, বেন এদের যে কোন একটি উল্লেখ থাকে Future Indefinite Tense', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">বাংলায় ক্রিয়ার শেষে বে, ব, বা, বি, বেন এদের যে কোন একটি উল্লেখ থাকে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Future Indefinite tense Structure</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Subject + shall/will + verb + object</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Future Indefinite tense examples&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- আমি কাজটি করিব- I will/shall do the work.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- তারা কাজটি করিবে- They will/shall do the work.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- আমি বিদ্যালয়ে যাব(যাবই)- I shall go to the school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- সে বিদ্যালয়ে যাবে(যাবেই)- He will go to the school.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- তারা বাজারে যাইবে(যাবে) &ndash; They will go to the market.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Note - সাধারনত 1st person এর পর shall বসতে পারে। এছাড়া অন্য সব ক্ষেত্রে will বসে।</span></span></span></p>', NULL, 'Future Indefinite Tense,Future Indefinite tense examples', 'future-indefinite-tense-kake-ble-future-indefinite-tense-examples-udahrn-sh-bistarit', 1, 26, '1', '2024-06-01 21:06:44', '2024-06-22 12:32:22'),
(97, 11, 'Future Continuous Tense কাকে বলে?  Future continuous tense Structure ।উদাহরণ সহ!', NULL, 'audio', 'ভবিষ্যৎ কালে কোন কাজ চলতে থাকবে এরূপ বোঝালে Future Continuous Tense Structure হয়। ভবিষ্যৎ কালে কোন কাজ চলতে থাকবে এরূপ বোঝালে Future continuous tense হয়। Subject + shall be/will be + verb এর সঙ্গে ing + object', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">ভবিষ্যৎ কালে কোন কাজ চলতে থাকবে এরূপ বোঝালে Future continuous tense হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">বাংলায় ক্রিয়ার শেষে তে থাকিব, তে থাকিবে, তে থাকিবা, তে থাকিবেন এদের যে কোন একটি যুক্ত থাকে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Future Continuous Tense Structure</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Subject + shall be/will be + </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">verb </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">এর </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">সঙ্গে</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">ing </span><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">+ object.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Future Continuous Tense Example :</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- আমি বইটি পড়িতে থাকিব &ndash; I shall be reading the book.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- আমি গান গাইতে থাকিব- I shall be singing the song.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- তারা ফুটবল খেলিতে থাকিবে- They will be playing football.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- সে কাজটি করিতে থাকিবে- He will be doing the work.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Future Continuous Tense Structure, Future Continuous Tense', 'future-continuous-tense-kake-ble-future-continuous-tense-structure-udahrn-sh', 1, 24, '1', '2024-06-01 21:13:26', '2024-06-21 04:56:40'),
(98, 11, 'Future Perfect Tense কাকে বলে?  উদাহরণ সহ! গঠনপ্রণালী', NULL, 'normal', 'ভবিষ্যৎ কালে কোন নির্দিষ্ট সময়ের মধ্যে কোন কাজ হয়ে যাবে বোঝালে বা দুটি কাজের মধ্যে একটি আগে হবে বোঝালে Future perfect tense হয়।', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">ভবিষ্যৎ কালে কোন নির্দিষ্ট সময়ের মধ্যে কোন কাজ হয়ে যাবে বোঝালে বা দুটি কাজের মধ্যে একটি আগে হবে বোঝালে Future perfect tense হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">ভবিষ্যৎ কালের দুটি কাজের মধ্যে যে কাজটি আগে হবে তা Future perfect tense হয় এবং পরেরটা simple present tense হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Future Perfect Tense&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Structure</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">1st subject + shall have/will have + verb এর past participle + 1st object + before + 2nd subject + main verb + 2nd object.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Future Perfect Tense&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Example</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- বাবা আসার আগে আমি কাজটি করিয়া থাকিব - I shall have done the work before my father comes.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- আমি বিকাল চারটার মধ্যে বইটি পড়িয়া থাকিব &ndash; I shall have finished reading the book by 4. P. m.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- তুমি যাওয়ার পূর্বে আমি গান গাইয়া থাকিব- I shall have sung a song before you leave.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- তারা আসার পূর্বে আমি পরা শেষ করিব &ndash; I shall have finished my lesson before they come.</span></span></span></p>', NULL, 'Future Perfect Tense , Future Perfect Tense example , Future Perfect Tense structure,', 'future-perfect-tense-kake-ble-udahrn-sh-gthnprnalee', 1, 21, '1', '2024-06-01 21:18:43', '2024-06-21 21:03:12'),
(99, 11, 'Future Perfect Continuous Tense কাকে বলে? উদাহরণ সহ! গঠনপ্রণালী Future Perfect Continuous Tense example', NULL, 'audio', 'ভবিষ্যৎ কালে কোন সময়ের মধ্যে কোন কাজ চলতে থাকবে এরূপ বোঝালে future perfect tense হয়।', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">ভবিষ্যৎ কালে কোন সময়ের মধ্যে কোন কাজ চলতে থাকবে এরূপ বোঝালে<span style=\"font-size:20px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">future perfect tense</span> </span>হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">ভবিষ্যৎ কালে দুটি কাজের মধ্যে যে কাজটি আগে চলতে থাকবে তা <span style=\"font-size:20px\">future perfect tense</span> হয় যে কাজটি পরে হবে তা<span style=\"font-size:20px\"> simple present tense</span> হয়।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">বাংলায় চিনার উপায়:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">বাংলায় ক্রিয়ার শেষে তে থাকিব, তে থাকিবে, তে থাকিবা, তে থাকিবেন এদের যে কোন একটি উল্লেখ থাকে।</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Future Perfect Continuous Tense Structure</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Subject &ndash; 1st subject + shall have been/will have been + verb এর সঙ্গে ing + 1st object + 2nd subject + main verb + 2nd object.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Future Perfect Continuous Tense Example</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- তুমি ফিরে না আসা পর্যন্ত আমরা তোমার জন্য অপেক্ষা করতে থাকব- <span style=\"font-size:20px\">we shall have been waiting for you until you come back.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- বাবা আসার আগে আমি কাজটি করিতে থাকিব-<span style=\"font-size:20px\"> I shall have been doing the work before my father comes.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- তারা আসার আগে আমি খেলিতে থাকিব-<span style=\"font-size:20px\"> I shall have been playing before they come.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">- সে ডিগ্রি পাওয়ার পূর্বে চার বছর ঢাকা বিশ্ববিদ্যালয়ে পড়তে থাকবে &ndash; <span style=\"font-size:20px\">he will have been studying at Dhaka university for four years before he gets degree.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Future Perfect Continuous Tense ,Future Perfect Continuous structure, Future Perfect Continuous Tense  example.', 'future-perfect-continuous-tense-kake-ble-udahrn-sh-gthnprnalee-future-perfect-continuous-tense-example', 1, 30, '1', '2024-06-01 21:23:14', '2024-06-22 13:32:06'),
(100, 11, 'Let\'s practice on future  tense চলুন present tense অনুশীলন করি', NULL, 'audio', 'Let\'s practice on future  tense চলুন present tense অনুশীলন করি', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">1. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">গুরুটি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;&nbsp;this cow </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">নুরুজ্জামান</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">জবাই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">করবে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp; Nuruzzaman will staughter&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ঈদের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">দিন</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">on<span style=\"color:black\"> Eid day&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ছুরি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ধারা</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">with knife&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সে</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">জবাই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">করিতে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">থাকিবে</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">He will be staughtering&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">যতক্ষণ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">পর্যন্ত</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">না</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">মরে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">গরুটি</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp; not until&nbsp;&nbsp; the cow dies </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">আমি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">গোসল</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">করিবো</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">দুপুর</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">২</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">টার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">মধ্যে</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">I shall have&nbsp; bathed by 2 p.m&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">গরুটি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">জবাইয়ের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">পর</span></span>&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">After the cow is slaughtered&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">আমি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">গোসত</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">কাটকাটি</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">করিতে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">থাকিব</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">৩</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ঘন্টা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ধরে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> I </span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">shall have been cutting meat for two hours.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">2. Birds will chatter / Tiger will be screaming / horse will have joined / in meeting by 4 p.m. / and / the lion will have been lead / for 3 hours / about animals right / in this animals meeting</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">পাখিরা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">কিলবিল</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">করবে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> / </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বাঘ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">চিৎকার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">করতে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">থাকবে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> / </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ঘোড়া</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">যোগ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">দেবে</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সভায়</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> / </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">বিকাল</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">৪</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">টার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">মধ্যে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> / </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এবং</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> / </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সিংহ</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">নেতৃত্ব</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">দেবে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> / </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">৩</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ঘন্টা</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">ধরে</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> / </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">প্রাণীদের</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">অধিকার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সম্পর্কিত</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\"> /</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">এই</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">সভার</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">মধ্যমে</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">3.</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Maria will decide to get a medical pedicure next week.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">মারিয়া আগামী সপ্তাহে একটি মেডিকেল পেডিকিউর করার সিদ্ধান্ত নেবে।</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Future Continuous:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">She will be visiting a specialist, who will be examining her feet carefully.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">সে একজন বিশেষজ্ঞের কাছে যাচ্ছে, যিনি তার পা ভালোভাবে পরীক্ষা করবেন।</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Future Perfect:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">By the time she finishes, they will have removed any dead skin and calluses.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">যখন সে শেষ করবে, তারা যেকোনো মৃত ত্বক এবং শক্ত চামড়া অপসারণ করে ফেলবে।</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Future Perfect Continuous:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Maria will have been feeling nervous, but the specialist will have been assuring her throughout the procedure.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">মারিয়া নার্ভাস অনুভব করবে, কিন্তু বিশেষজ্ঞ তাকে প্রক্রিয়া চলাকালীন আশ্বস্ত করতে থাকবে।</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Future Simple:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Her feet will feel lighter and more comfortable.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">তার পা হালকা এবং আরো আরামদায়ক মনে হবে।</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Future Continuous:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">After the procedure, the specialist will be giving Maria tips.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">প্রক্রিয়ার পর, বিশেষজ্ঞ মারিয়াকে পরামর্শ দেবেন।</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Future Perfect:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Maria will have followed the advice and will notice her feet are healthier.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">মারিয়া পরামর্শগুলি অনুসরণ করেছে এবং লক্ষ্য করবে তার পা আরো সুস্থ।</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Future Perfect Continuous:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">She will have been grateful for the medical pedicure and will have been taking care of her feet.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">সে মেডিকেল পেডিকিউরের জন্য কৃতজ্ঞ থাকবে এবং তার পায়ের যত্ন নিতে থাকবে।</span></span></p>', NULL, 'Let\'s practice on future  tense', 'lets-practice-on-future-tense-clun-present-tense-onuseeln-kri', 1, 24, '1', '2024-06-01 21:30:42', '2024-06-21 08:39:51');
