le=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">it<strong><span style=\"color:#129b50\">&#39;s</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:80.25pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">it is&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#cd4b3c\">not</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:196.9pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">it<strong><span style=\"color:#129b50\">&#39;s</span></strong>&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#cd4b3c\">not</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:196.9pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">it&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#129b50\">is</span><span style=\"color:#cd4b3c\">n&#39;t</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:75.25pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">we&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#129b50\">are</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:106.6pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">we<strong><span style=\"color:#129b50\">&#39;re</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:80.25pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">