<strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#5f490d\">Long form</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"background-color:#f9f6eb; width:108.1pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#5f490d\">Contracted form</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width:95.65pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">I, we, you, they</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:75.25pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">I&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#129b50\">do</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:106.6pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">---</span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:81.6pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">we&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#129b50\">do</span></strong>&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#cd4b3c\">not</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width:108.1pt\">\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">we&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#129b50\">do</span><span style=\"color:#cd4