(137, '2', 'md.ruhulaminsarker43770', 'MD. RUHUL AMIN SARKER', 'ruhul.jnu11@gmail.com', NULL, 'teacher', 1, 0, '$2y$10$ry4NVkItpe8XwKRAr6jyAeFRoNnwzrsf7w3IsIW9Xo.KlvSkaSuK6', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-25', 'yes', 10, 'undefined', NULL, 'undefined', 'undefined', NULL, 'undefined', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/ruhol.amin.3766?mibextid=LQQJ4d', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I teach Economics of graphs and math as your tutor', '-18-OzMM106rns', 'Any type of math and all chapter in economics . I will cover to take off a good number in your  academic exam.', '5000/ monthly', '4/week', '1.5 hour', 'students place', 'offline', 'Both batch and individual', '8 to 11', NULL, '3 to 9 pm', 'Bangla and English', 'Available', 'Hi! I am Ruhul Amin. I would describe myself as a positive, energetic, knowledgeable, and industrious teacher. I have a flexible style of teaching that can cater to all students and abilities. I would also say that I am a high-achieving teacher. I can teach economics properly with making understood of graphs and math related to the subject.', 'Initially, I worked at a private School  for three years, where I had the opportunity to teach economics to Enter level students while also focusing on economics. Additionally, I had the privilege of being a sponsor for extracurricular or volunteer work.', 'Master\'s', '2023', 'Jagannath University', 'Economics', '3.2', NULL, 'Bangladesh', 'Dhaka', 'Dhaka', 'Sutrapur', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Under review for 72 hours.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bs7hKZGr41fH5B2MNkcLMBvOJQUul3VIHwNPVzXsM8xrxCzF.jpg', '2024-05-23 04:56:02', '2024-05-25 21:43:43'),
(138, '2', 'mdatiqurrahman70076', 'MD ATIQUR RAHMAN', 'misbahatiq2@gmail.com', NULL, 'general', 1, 1, '$2y$10$DGBOecfD0rt0UrzVSuf8ROFoRpw1o3RbCfO94J0jEeT6TUwLoVI/2', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-23', 'no', 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-23 13:25:24', '2024-05-23 13:25:24'),
(139, '2', 'mdatiqurrahman83145', 'MD ATIQUR RAHMAN', 'atiqcdut1@gmail.com', NULL, 'teacher', 1, 0, '$2y$10$j0Y.SN6ys.VsM1ooblzFF.AUP8dcqguIJGgo.vqSAJTKiqdVjYpQq', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-25', 'yes', 10, 'undefined', NULL, '15-01-2000', 'Male', NULL, '+8613258183550', 'Permanent : Tulagaon, Sultanpur, debidwar, Cumilla, chittagong, Bangladesh. \npresent :  Chengdu university of technology No1 Er xian qiao, Chenghua, Chengdu, Sichuan, China', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '+880 1602-681927', 'https://www.facebook.com/md.atiqurrahman.7902564?mibextid=ZbWKwL', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Learn Chinese Online for Bengali Speakers with Atik', '-1-90TgfgzX6p', 'Join Atik\'s online Chinese classes tailored for Bengali speakers. Simplify learning with bilingual lessons, practical vocabulary, and cultural insight', '5000', '4/week', '2 hours', 'students place', 'online', 'Both batch and individual', 'any person', NULL, '3 to 9 pm', 'Bangla', 'Available', 'Assalamo alaikom orahmatollahi obarkatoho!\r\n\r\nI am MD Atiqur Rahman, a 25-year-old student originally from Cumilla, Bangladesh. Currently, I reside in China, pursuing my master\'s degree at Chengdu University of Technology. I am proficient in both English and Chinese, having earned my HSK-5 certification, which attests to my advanced proficiency in the Chinese language. Since 2019, I have been living in China, immersing myself in the academic and cultural landscape of this fascinating country.\r\n\r\nLiving in China for the past few years has provided me with a wealth of experience and insights into various aspects of Chinese life. I have become well-acquainted with the local lifestyle, job market, and cultural habits of the Chinese people. The lifestyle here is dynamic and fast-paced, particularly in urban centers like Chengdu. People are industrious and place a high value on education and professional success. This has been evident in the rigorous academic environment at my university and the competitive job market.\r\n\r\nUnderstanding Chinese culture has been a remarkable journey. The Chinese people have a rich cultural heritage, and their traditions are deeply embedded in daily life. From celebrating festivals like the Spring Festival (Chinese New Year) to engaging in practices such as Tai Chi in the parks, I have witnessed the blend of ancient traditions with modern living. The emphasis on family, respect for elders, and the communal spirit are significant cultural traits that I have come to appreciate.\r\n\r\nMoreover, the job market in China is diverse and offers numerous opportunities, especially for those who are proficient in Chinese and possess relevant skills. There is a strong demand for professionals in technology, engineering, and education, reflecting the country’s rapid economic growth and development.\r\n\r\nOverall, my time in China has been immensely enriching, allowing me to gain a deeper understanding of the country’s culture and its people. This experience has not only broadened my academic and professional horizons but also enriched my personal life, providing me with lasting memories and invaluable lessons.', 'I offer a unique and easy way to learn Chinese online, specifically tailored for Bengali learners. 从一开始到水平在网上希望学习中文语音的所有的同学可以学。 Every single student who wants to learn Chinese online, from the beginning to proficiency, can learn here. Having lived in China since 2019 and being certified with HSK-5, I combine my deep understanding of the Chinese language and culture with my native Bengali language skills to create an effective learning experience.\r\n\r\nMy teaching method focuses on simplifying Chinese language learning for Bengali speakers. My approach includes:\r\n\r\nBilingual Instruction: Lessons are conducted in Bengali, making it easier for students to grasp complex Chinese concepts without language barriers.\r\n\r\nPractical Vocabulary: I emphasize practical vocabulary and everyday phrases, helping students quickly become conversational in real-life situations.\r\n\r\nCultural Insights: Understanding Chinese culture is integral to learning the language. I incorporate cultural lessons, providing students with a comprehensive understanding of both language and customs.\r\n\r\nInteractive Sessions: Through interactive online sessions, I engage students in speaking, listening, and writing exercises, ensuring a well-rounded learning experience.\r\n\r\nCustomized Learning Plans: Recognizing that each student has unique learning needs, I offer personalized lesson plans tailored to individual goals and proficiency levels.\r\n\r\nWhether you are a beginner or looking to improve your existing Chinese skills, my Bengali-medium Chinese lessons provide an accessible and enjoyable way to master the language. Join my online classes and embark on a rewarding journey of learning Chinese from the comfort of your home.', 'Undergraduate.', '2024', 'Chengdu university of technology', 'Tourism management,', '3.56', NULL, 'Bangladesh', 'Dhaka', 'Dhaka', 'Other', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'congratulations for being a teacher', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I9HJ0hZuQSpeRmlhrIkDPIlRoWg48fqTJnsAsj3570NBjg5Y.jpg', '2024-05-23 13:25:48', '2024-05-27 04:07:21'),
(140, '2', 'shouravraj31696', 'Shourav Rajbongshi', 'shouravrajb.999@gmail.com', NULL, 'teacher', 1, 0, '$2y$10$CQBO0eXvYZvogGsyzMgNKOEr0bqxRHiOAvTKY8WqX1VOo4USlYp0K', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-10', 'yes', 9998, 'undefined', NULL, '2001-02-25', 'male', NULL, '01932376388', 'Nawabgonj-1320, Dhaka-1, Banladesh', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '+8801932376388', 'https://www.facebook.com/developer.shourav', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/developer-shourav', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Web Development, ICT, Fronted Development', 'web-development-ict-fronted-development', 'Empowering students with skills in web development, ICT fundamentals, and frontend technologies for a digital future.***** frontend developer, I bring', '8000', '3 days / week', '45 min', 'Teacher Home', 'Offline', 'Batch', 'From High School', NULL, '8am to 10 am', 'English', 'Available', 'As an experienced Web Developer and ICT Teacher, I am passionate about shaping the future of technology through education. With a strong background in frontend development, I strive to empower students with the skills needed to excel in the digital world. My teaching approach combines practical coding exercises, real-world projects, and up-to-date industry insights, ensuring students are well-equipped for their careers. \r\n\r\nI believe in fostering a collaborative and engaging learning environment where students can explore their creativity and develop problem-solving skills. Join me on a journey to master web development and ICT, and unlock your potential in the ever-evolving tech landscape. *** frontend developer, I bring current, practical insights into the classroom, helping students bridge the gap between theory and  practice. frontend developer, I bring current, practical insights into the classroom, helping students bridge the gap between theory and  practice. frontend developer, I bring current, practical insights into the classroom, helping students bridge the gap between theory and  practice.frontend developer, I bring current, practical insights into the classroom, helping students bridge the gap between theory and  practice.frontend developer, I bring current, practical insights into the classroom, helping students bridge the gap between theory and  practice.', 'With over 4 years of experience in ICT and web development, I have guided students through topics from basic computer literacy to advanced web development. My hands-on teaching approach emphasizes real-world application and continuous assessment. As a frontend developer, I bring current, practical insights into the classroom, helping students bridge the gap between theory and  practice. **** frontend developer, I bring current, practical insights into the classroom, helping students bridge the gap between theory and  practice.', 'BBA', '2024', 'National University', 'Accounting', '3.45', NULL, 'Bangladesh', 'Dhaka', 'Dhaka', 'Jatrabari', 'Nawabgonj', 'Kolakopa', 'Kashimpur', '64-E', 1, 'congratulations for being a honorable teacher', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1718018862-o06h6DVs8Lf1wEwGmSp2XXWOiZ5kQK8k.png', '2024-05-23 14:58:13', '2024-06-22 19:03:44'),
