(142, '2', 'jahirulislam59129', 'JAHIRUL Islam', 'rjahir372@gmail.com', NULL, 'teacher', 1, 0, '$2y$10$llhCUtcxw5/OMfABKTnzgORuCX7j8hAUniuqcuQzByvbi7AEBevga', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-03', 'yes', 10, 'undefined', NULL, 'undefined', 'undefined', NULL, 'undefined', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I tech Economics , English, match and ICT', '-1-zPnAThWYpm', 'I instruct in Economics, English, Math and ICT, providing a cohesive learning experience and fostering a diverse skill set through a multidisciplinary', '3000', '5/ weekly', '1.5 hour', 'student home', 'both online and off-line', 'Batch and individual both', '7 to 12', NULL, 'from 9 am to 9 pm', 'Bangla', 'available', 'I am Md Jahir,  graduate from Comilla Victoria College under National University, achieved a CGPA of 3.19 in 2020. I have expertise in English, Economics, Math, and ICT, making me a versatile candidate for a teaching position. my multidisciplinary knowledge allows me to provide a comprehensive and integrated learning experience. my proficiency in these subjects ensures that students receive quality education across various fields, fostering a diverse skill set. my academic background and expertise make me an excellent candidate for teaching positions,', 'I have 8 years of experience as a home tutor, known for being a caring teacher. my  effectively teaches all subjects, providing personalized and comprehensive instruction to students of various levels, ensuring their academic growth and success.', 'M.S.S', '2020', 'National University', 'Economic', '3.19', NULL, 'Bangladesh', 'Chattogram', 'Cumilla', 'Comilla sadar', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Under review for 72 hours.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1717433923-vZm1pAfi0bhsdhleWm2herEZDlvA8LRI.jpg', '2024-05-26 01:13:11', '2024-06-04 03:27:19'),
