(146, '2', 'saddam59687', 'Saddam', 'saifisaddam395@gamil.com', NULL, 'teacher', 0, 0, '$2y$10$97ENagJXSflKmB22jbi2sujDHNXWBzW3t0upJRvJfSEIvl.lZlHMC', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-04', 'yes', 10, 'undefined', NULL, '30/1/1996', 'Male', NULL, '01715861762', 'Cumilla, Cantonment', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'English, Arabic', '-1-de59oGpJUK', 'First of all,My education background  is Madrasha but I know good English because I am a English teacher of alim madrasha.', '4000', '5 days', '1 hour', 'Student home and teachers home but it will be dependent of salary', 'Offline', 'Batch and individual', 'Class 8 to 10', NULL, 'Evening', 'English medium Arabic', 'available', 'My key points of teaching \n1. All problems of micro and macro English will be solved.\n2. Fundamentals of English  will be taught simply.\n3.  Classes will be arranged according to topic.\n4. Each topic will be explained simply.\n5. Math and English  presented simply.\n6. Each class will be of 1 hour duration.\n7. Classes will be held 5 days a week.\n8. For class 12th the course will be completed through 60 classes in 3 months and extension of classes till the completion of the course for Honors general subjects.\n9.3 month course is enough for students to get good results in English.', 'Alhamdulillah, I have teaching experience of 4 years. Because I was in 2 coaching centers. I stopped all after joining madrasa. Of course in addition to this I teach 2 classes in my madrasa. They study class 8 to 10 in a year. I hope if any student studies with me I will try my best from my position to give him something good.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bangladesh', 'Chattogram', 'Cumilla', 'Burichang', 'Rampur', 'Varella', 'Rampur', NULL, 2, 'Under review for 72 hours.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1717494309-5FRxnB1ASmdknvVG4FI8Y3dtoVgNhj6t.jpg', '2024-06-04 19:20:53', '2024-06-10 19:45:46');
