(147, '2', 'md.manzurhosen31708', 'MD. Manzur hosen', 'gazimonjur01@gmail.com', NULL, 'teacher', 1, 0, '$2y$10$/1rMFJOFkPxriipN/gB7l.sMGWe/KqdHaDVSZFe.10lKcvAO5pc4a', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-09', 'yes', 10, 'undefined', NULL, 'undefined', 'undefined', NULL, 'undefined', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '01686740893', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I teach micro and macro economics for undergraduate students', '-1-tGnF7hDI16', 'My key point of teaching: 1. All problems of micro and macro economy will be solved. 2. Fundamentals of economics will be taught simpl', '2000', '36 days', '1 hour', 'Student Home', 'online and offline', 'Online based', 'High School & Hon\'s', NULL, '3 to 11 pm', 'Bengali Medium', 'Available', 'I am Md. Manzur Hosen \r\n from BegBirkhal, Kaduty Bazar, Chandina ,Cumilla, Bangladesh. \r\nI am a practical Muslim . Teaching is my professional part of my life . I have been giving home tutor . Online tutor . Service almost for 5 years individually or batch . I am responsible for making my students to get a satisfaction  marks in their academics exam .  So please just text me and connect with me.', 'My key points of teaching \r\n1. All problems of micro and macro economy will be solved.\r\n2. Fundamentals of economics will be taught simply.3.  Classes will be arranged according to topic.\r\n4. Each topic will be explained simply.\r\n5. Math and geometry present simply.\r\n6. Each class will be of 1 hour duration.\r\n7. Classes will be held 3 days a week.\r\n8. For class 12th the course will be completed through 36 classes in 3 months and extension of classes till the completion of the course for Honors general subjects.\r\n9. three months course is enough for students to get good results in economics.', 'Post graduate', '2019', 'Comilla victoria gov\'t college', 'Mss', '3.3', NULL, 'Bangladesh', 'Chattogram', 'Cumilla', 'Chandina', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'ok', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1717951735-4J1NjXjghv9Z3fHwrbBy0